Class SourceIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.util.SourceIterator

  • public class SourceIterator
extends java.lang.Object
    FYI this class is based on ReadableChannelIterator and can be full featured substitution in the future UPDATE: ReadableChannelIterator has meanwhile evolved. It now handles namely preferred data source types Parser.DataSourceType.
